<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="similarProvisions" id="id5fdbbbbf-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Similar Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Similar provisions were contained in <ref href="/us/pl/102/381/tI">Pub. L. 102–381, title I</ref>, <date date="1992-10-05">Oct. 5, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/1378">106 Stat. 1378</ref>, 1379.</p>
